bib_record.title: Polarization and differential cross section for elastic scattering of 40-MeV protons. II

free_txt: A polarized proton beam was produced by scattering
50-MeV protons from a 10-MeV thick calcium target.
NaI(Tl) crystals mounted on selected RCA 6199
Uncertainty in determining the target thickness
A polarized proton beam was produced by scattering
50-MeV protons from a 10-MeV thick calcium target.
Energy spread in the range 300 to 500 keV.
The over-all resolution was 500 to 800 keV.
Polarization and differential cross-section for elastic
scattering of 40-MeV protons from C-12, Ca-40, Ni-58,
Zr-90 and Pb-208 and experimental method was described.
